{
  "stem": "4919.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They didn't tell anything, they started to laugh on him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But at the same very moment the old man come in, and he started to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He said, it's my relative.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He lives nearby, at the-- at the next village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It's my relatives.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know, and-- and I was lucky again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But after that, I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I walked away, and I fell down on the field, fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And again, I was sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it was the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And now the last episode.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was-- so I walked further, again, to the Don River.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "At the one side of the Don River, at the west side, there have been the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "At the east side, the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I was dreaming again to cross the river and to join the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came up to a small village, and a woman was outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, Come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't the only one, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People like me used to wandering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I approach her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said, Are you hungry?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was always hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She gave me borscht, she gave me fried bread, I remember, fresh warm bread, she gave me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she didn't look like a peasant, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I saw she's from a city, but I didn't ask question.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so-- and so she-- And then, after that, she gave me a piece of bread, and said to me, Are you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But be careful here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There are a lot of here, Germans, police, and Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And even the Hungarians, they-- they are worse than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went only 100 feet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A Hungarian soldier grabbed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- she-- and she saw that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
